---
description: "Enforces Rust handler/module/struct naming, file placement, and async main signatures for functions in src/, lib/, and handler.rs. Applies to .rs files."
globs: "src/**/*.rs,lib/**/*.rs"
alwaysApply: true
---
- Ensure all Lambda handlers use the pattern:
  `use lambda_runtime::{service_fn, LambdaEvent, Error};`
  `#[tokio::main]`
  `async fn main() -> Result<(), Error>`
- Require module+file name match for entities (`lib/composer/src/aws/function.rs` -> `Function` struct).
- Prohibit duplicate struct names in a module.
